## Limitations

The report is based on available online resources and may not cover all possible governmental strategies for environmental protection. The information is limited to the perspectives and data provided by the selected sources. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of environmental policies means that new strategies and technologies may emerge that are not covered in this report.